WRIGHT v. REUSENS et al. (Supreme Court, General Term, Second Department. December 1, 1893.) Action by James R. Wright against Gillaume A. Reusens and others.

Argued before DYKMAN, PRATT, and CULLEN, JJ.

No opinion. Motion for reargument denied, with leave to go to the court of appeals. See 21 N. Y. Supp. 485.
